                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150215-16-off83 t18150215-16-crimeloc85"></join>. On Friday, the 10th of February, about half past eight in the evening, I heard my errand boy cry stop thief; I went to the door; I saw the boy pursuing the man, and when I attempted to stop the prisoner, he presented a knife at me, one of the articles he had taken.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18150215-16-person197">
                  JOHN 
                  STEVENS
               <interp inst="t18150215-16-person197" type="surname" value="STEVENS"></interp>
